data.description: Downtown Delight!  Imagine yourself unwinding after a long day at work enjoying the Thread Walking Trail located just a hop and a skip from your front door!  This Meticulously Maintained and Charming 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath home is Sure to Please your Entire Family!  Features include; split bedroom design, Gorgeous Hardwood Flooring, Spacious Design, Stadium Size Back Yard offering an abundance of parking so Rare to Find Downtown, Brand New Roof, Updated Kitchen, Generous Size Living Area, Screened Porch, Inspiring Landscape adorned with Mature Oaks, LaGrange District, Premier Location just a short stroll from all that our Vibrant Downtown has to offer, Abundance of Storage and Shop Space and Too Many other features to mention!  Call your Favorite Realtor Today to Learn More- You Are Sure to Gain Hero Status Among Your Family when you claim this Highly Sought After Address as your very own!
